@startuml
title Add Client Address Algorithm

actor Client
participant "Controller" as Controller
participant "Mediator" as Mediator
participant "Handler" as Handler
participant "Repository" as Repository
database DB

Client -> Controller: POST /api/clients/{id}/addresses
Controller -> Mediator: Send(CreateClientAddressCommand)
Mediator -> Handler: Handle command
Handler -> Repository: AddAsync(entity)
Repository -> DB: INSERT client_address
DB --> Repository: Returns created entity
Repository --> Handler: ClientAddress
Handler --> Mediator: ClientAddressDto
Mediator --> Controller: ClientAddressDto
Controller --> Client: 201 Created
@enduml
